VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(CSRF|XSS|SQLi)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(?i)(ToLower|ToUpper) && MISSING:(?i)(sanitize|escape|encode|prepared|parameterized)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects standard mitigation techniques for CSRF, XSS, and SQL injection vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Miscellaneous Webapp Mitigations: CSRF, XSS, SQL Injection.
